{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1019","heading":"Definitions","label":"1019 Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/ch28/schI/ptE","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsA prior section 1019, , as added , , , authorized appropriations for education outreach programs, prior to the general amendment of this subchapter by .Pub. L. 89–329, title I, § 119Pub. L. 96–374, title I, § 101(a)94 Stat. 1383Pub. L. 99–498Oct. 3, 1980"],"amendments":["Prior ProvisionsA prior section 1019, , as added , , , authorized appropriations for education outreach programs, prior to the general amendment of this subchapter by .Pub. L. 89–329, title I, § 119Pub. L. 96–374, title I, § 101(a)94 Stat. 1383Pub. L. 99–498Oct. 3, 1980"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Agent","label":"1 Agent","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “agent” means an officer or employee of a covered institution or an institution-affiliated organization.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Covered institution","label":"2 Covered institution","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “covered institution” means any institution of higher education, as such term is defined in , that receives any Federal funding or assistance.section 1002 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Education loan","label":"3 Education loan","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any loan made, insured, or guaranteed under part B of subchapter IV;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any loan made under part D of subchapter IV; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a private education loan.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Eligible lender","label":"4 Eligible lender","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “eligible lender” has the meaning given such term in .section 1085(d) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Institution-affiliated organization","label":"5 Institution-affiliated organization","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F5%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F5%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is directly or indirectly related to a covered institution; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F5%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is engaged in the practice of recommending, promoting, or endorsing education loans for students attending such covered institution or the families of such students;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F5%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"may include an alumni organization, athletic organization, foundation, or social, academic, or professional organization, of a covered institution; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F5%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"notwithstanding subparagraphs (A) and (B), does not include any lender with respect to any education loan secured, made, or extended by such lender.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":"Lender","label":"6 Lender","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F6%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F6%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of a loan made, insured, or guaranteed under part B of subchapter IV, an eligible lender;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F6%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of any loan issued or provided to a student under part D of subchapter IV, the Secretary; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F6%2FA%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of a private education loan, a private educational lender as defined in ; andsection 1650 of title 15","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F6%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"includes any other person engaged in the business of securing, making, or extending education loans on behalf of the lender.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":"Officer","label":"7 Officer","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “officer” includes a director or trustee of a covered institution or institution-affiliated organization, if such individual is treated as an employee of such covered institution or institution-affiliated organization, respectively.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"8","heading":"Preferred lender arrangement","label":"8 Preferred lender arrangement","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"under which a lender provides or otherwise issues education loans to the students attending such covered institution or the families of such students; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"that relates to such covered institution or such institution-affiliated organization recommending, promoting, or endorsing the education loan products of the lender; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"arrangements or agreements with respect to loans under part D of subchapter IV; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/8/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F8%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"arrangements or agreements with respect to loans that originate through the auction pilot program under .section 1099d(b) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"9","heading":"Private education loan","label":"9 Private education loan","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019/9","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1019","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1019%2F9","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “private education loan” has the meaning given the term in .section 1650 of title 15","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
